data.description: Five-bedroom home on a double lot! Spacious two story home in Chenango Bridge features a large living room with wood burning fireplace and a pellet stove for supplemental heat and to keep heating costs low, formal dining room and updated kitchen with doors to the enclosed porch and fenced in large back yard.  Two bedrooms and a full bathroom on the first floor and three bedrooms and a full bathroom on the second floor including the large master suite with walk-in closet. Oversized two car garage with workshop area.
